value.name: Outpouring of grief for 'hero' San Jose officer killed on duty
value.description: Johnson’s alleged shooter, 57-year-old Scott Dunham, was later discovered dead from a gunshot wound. Authorities were looking into whether he was killed by police gunfire or took his own life.
